{"tid":2364613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"55被捕者手機送中　美媒：黑客技術助破新iPhone","createTime":"2021-01-13T06:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T08:51:29.000Z","uid":177047,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f00114545e2f83973f0992df0fb6dac5d1cd78f9","tid":2364613,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:26:32.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】警方國安處上周大規模拘捕55名民主派初選協調者及參加者，不少被捕人反映手機出現異常活動。《華盛頓郵報》昨日報道，有關行動撿走逾200部手機和電子設備，並引述香港警隊消息指，警方無法破解較新型號的iPhone，將撿走的被捕人士手機及電子設備送往內地破解，因為中國有更先進的黑客技術竊取手機資訊。有被捕人士直言，相信警方有將他的手機「送中」，保釋後也發現「與政府有聯繫的人士」曾嘗試登入他的賬户。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/CKMPSHHFOJA45NTGA73GAOF4GA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FCKMPSHHFOJA45NTGA73GAOF4GA%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=95fac160\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210113%2FCKMPSHHFOJA45NTGA73GAOF4GA%2F&h=ff8721b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210113/CKMPSHHFOJA45NTGA73GAOF4GA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗數據送中，直接將手機電腦物理送中，所以狗隻比返你都係唔好要，寧願買過部"},{"pid":"e17f157cf1ca56caf80d2a6760655fa161d0b2c3","tid":2364613,"uid":144626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:30:08.000Z","msg":"呢D就係美國堆大學STEM長久以來教出嚟畜牲做嘅好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e506e1aced4ed21a9597f49d756106652c4d43","tid":2364613,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"咁大件事冇人講<img src=\"/a